>> source: https://www.homegrounds.co/how-to-use-a-french-press/
>> prep time: 1 minute
>> cook time: 7 minutes

Fill your #mug most of the way with @water{} and #microwave for ~{2%minutes} or until just below boiling.

Pour about 1/16 as much @coffee grounds{} as you have water into your #french press{}.

Pour your hot water into the french press. Stir, place the top on, and wait for ~{4%minutes}.

Slowly push down the plunger and pour off the coffee into your mug.
